Here are the Setps to Create TelegramBot using ESP32:

Step 1: Download Telegram and Login into it.

Step 2: In Telegram Search @BotFather and click on Start.

Step 3: click on /newbot, give name to your bot, now your bot is created.

Step 4: You will find the bot link and HTTP API, note both.

Step 5: Search in Telegram @myidbot, click on start, then click on /getid, note your id.

Step 6: Install Arduino IDE, add ESP32 preference link, Download ESP32 boards.

Step 7: Open Create_Telegram_Bot.ino, in the code replace wifi ssid & password, replace your telegram http api and chat id.

Step 8: Add your project logic in handleNewMessages().
